  "ruleTexts": {
    "Precision": "Each time an attack made with this weapon targets a unit containing a Character, the attacking player can allocate that attack to a Character model in that unit.",
    "Anti-Infantry 4+": "An unmodified Wound roll of 4+ scores a Critical Wound against a target with the Infantry keyword.",
    "Assault": "This weapon can be shot even if the bearer's unit Advanced this turn.",
    "Heavy": "Each time an attack is made with this weapon, if the bearer's unit Remained Stationary this turn, add 1 to that attack's Hit roll.",
    "Pistol": "This weapon can be shot even while the bearer's unit is within Engagement Range of enemy units."
  },
